text: Like a hotel 5 star... I like the pool so much.. Very clean and good maintained.. And also they got hot pool water... Best pool ever

1.Our Suite was in good condition..clean..kitchen utensils provided..
2.Big swimming pool  but due to cmco..only 1 hour allowed to swim prior on early booking slot
3.the admin at the frontdesk quite rude..(lady)...having difficulty comunicate with her...as if we are staying there for free..wifi password only given upon asking n she got no manners at all..miscommunication between the front desk n sucurity..and we became the victim..sorry ur front desk ..only 1/10 rated as 4 the rudeness n bad experience we had...the rest..hotel ..aprtment was good...
